# Prerequisites: Visual Studio & C++
######################################

# Visual Studio Architecture & Temp files
.vs/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
out/
build/

# Compilation objects and libraries
*.obj
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.lib
*.dll
*.exp
*.pch
*.idb
*.tlog
