# Visual Studio User Files
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# OpenCV / Dependency folders (if they are inside your project folder)
# Usually, you keep OpenCV in C:/, but if it's in your project, ignore it:
# bin/
# lib/

# C++ Precompiled headers
*.pch

# Temporary files created by VS
*.aps
*.ncb
*.opendb
*.sdf
*.cache
*.ipch
*.log